sentence: where is denny's in the bay area ?
sentence-with-vars: where is VARrest in the VARregion ?
sql: select RESTAURANT.NAME,LOCATION.HOUSE_NUMBER from GEOGRAPHIC,RESTAURANT,LOCATION where GEOGRAPHIC.CITY_NAME=RESTAURANT.CITY_NAME and RESTAURANT.NAME='denny's' and GEOGRAPHIC.REGION='bay area' and LOCATION.RESTAURANT_ID=RESTAURANT.ID
sql-with-vars: select RESTAURANT.NAME,LOCATION.HOUSE_NUMBER from GEOGRAPHIC,RESTAURANT,LOCATION where GEOGRAPHIC.CITY_NAME=RESTAURANT.CITY_NAME and RESTAURANT.NAME='VARrest' and GEOGRAPHIC.REGION='VARregion' and LOCATION.RESTAURANT_ID=RESTAURANT.ID
